  src/cli/commands/calendar.ts,project,calendar implementation verified
close_reason: "All calendar views (agenda/day/week/month) tested with recurrence expansion, boundary clipping, output format switching, and occurrence limiting"
body: "Key findings: (1) Default agenda view correctly expands recurring events across 365-day lookahead. (2) Week view anchors to Monday-Sunday. (3) Month view uses full UTC month boundaries. (4) Summary counts accurately segment by-kind (deadline/reminder/event), by-type, by-status, and recurring_events. (5) Event start= field is correct (not start_at=). (6) Calendar defaults to markdown output as designed. (7) --occurrence-limit correctly bounds expansion. (8) Context command integrates agenda data."
